# Roadmap — {{project_name}}

Where this project could go. Items here are aspirations, not commitments — a place to capture ideas, inspiration, and future directions without the pressure of a deadline.

When an item gets evaluated, the outcome is logged in [DECISIONS.md](DECISIONS.md). This creates a traceable pipeline from idea to decision.

**Statuses:** `active` (in progress) · `idea` (worth evaluating) · `parked` (inspiration, no timeline) · `decided` (evaluated — see DECISIONS.md)

